---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - Takoyaki Cloud">
  <section class="border-b py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-6">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground">Last updated: February 2026</p>

      <div class="mt-10 space-y-8 text-sm leading-6 text-muted-foreground [&_h2]:mt-10 [&_h2]:text-base [&_h2]:font-semibold [&_h2]:text-foreground">
        <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We collect information you provide when creating an account: name, email, and billing information. We also collect usage data such as server metrics and IP addresses for service delivery and security.</p>

        <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use your information to provide and maintain our Services, process payments, communicate about your account, provide support, and improve our Services. We do not sell your personal information.</p>

        <h2>3. Data Storage and Security</h2>
        <p>We implement appropriate security measures to protect your data. Credentials are stored using industry-standard encryption. Payment processing is handled by PCI-compliant third-party processors.</p>

        <h2>4. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>We may use third-party services for payment processing, analytics, and communication. We only share the minimum information necessary.</p>

        <h2>5. Cookies</h2>
        <p>Our website uses essential cookies for authentication and preferences (such as dark mode). We do not use third-party tracking or advertising cookies.</p>

        <h2>6. Data Retention</h2>
        <p>We retain account information for as long as your account is active. After deletion, we may retain certain data as required by law.</p>

        <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal information. <a href="/contact" class="text-rose-500 hover:text-rose-600">Contact us</a> to exercise these rights.</p>

        <h2>8. Changes</h2>
        <p>We may update this policy from time to time. Material changes will be communicated via email.</p>

        <h2>9. Contact</h2>
        <p>Questions? <a href="/contact" class="text-rose-500 hover:text-rose-600">Contact us</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
